      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this impeccably preserved vehicle, which stands as a testament to rigorous maintenance and fastidious ownership. The exterior retains its original showroom luster, complemented by an interior that remains in superlative condition, free from wear or blemish. This unit has undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure it meets our most exacting mechanical standards. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who accepts only the finest examples, this vehicle offers an unrivaled opportunity to acquire a specimen of true distinction.",
      "price": 48500.0,
