    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve gotta see this absolute stunner. Honestly, it looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014it's been pampered since day one! Not a single scratch or smudge to be found, and the interior still has that fresh new-car smell. It's a total dream to drive and truly in pristine shape. I\u2019m so excited for whoever gets to take this beauty home!",
