      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle of unparalleled distinction. This specimen has been maintained to an exacting standard, preserved in showroom condition with an interior and exterior that remain virtually indistinguishable from new. Every mechanical component has been rigorously inspected to ensure it meets our uncompromising criteria for excellence. For the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection, this offering represents the pinnacle of its class.",
